<p>Success!
While for_each may seem new and frightening and weird and unintuitive, it‚Äôs also (for now) the only sensible option if you don‚Äôt want to be surprised by unintended downtime or scaling issues down the line.</p>

<p>Thank you for staying with us through this very specific (but hopefully useful) adventure.</p>

